#. tr: Windows XP or earlier. Has Thumbs.db scattered throughout the system.
#: ../src/win32/config/CacheTab.cpp:193
msgctxt "CacheTab"
msgid "If any image type settings were changed, you will need to clear the thumbnail cache files.\n"
"This version of Windows does not have a centralized thumbnail database, so it may take a while for all Thumbs.db files to be located and deleted."
msgstr "If any image type settings were changed, you will need to clear the thumbnail cache files.\n"
"This version of Windows does not have a centralised thumbnail database, so it may take a while for all Thumbs.db files to be located and deleted."

